<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>10250</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>15625</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>国王敲了敲扶手，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>15625</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>21690</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>看向王后：“我们要怎么让艾伦哭呢？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>21691</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>26408</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那是不可能的！”王后叹了口气，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>26409</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>29662</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“她只会笑！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>29662</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>35361</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是，王后很快有了一个主意。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>35361</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>39163</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第二天，一个乞丐来到了王宫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>39163</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>41146</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他穿着破烂的衣服，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>41146</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>44989</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>脸上全是泥土，脏兮兮的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>44990</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>49957</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>仆人领着艾伦过来了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>49957</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>53630</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你找我吗，爸爸？”艾伦问国王。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>53630</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>57126</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>国王向艾伦介绍乞丐。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>57127</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>59829</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这个人的生活非常可怜，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>59829</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>62018</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>现在来听一听他的故事吧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>62019</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69097</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>国王转向乞丐，“请告诉我们你最悲伤的故事。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69097</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>74654</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>接下来，这个乞丐告诉了艾伦他有多么可怜：</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>74654</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>80743</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“每天晚上都饿着肚子睡觉，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>80743</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>84733</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>躺在冰冷的地上，又饿又冷。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>84733</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>94874</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有时候几天只吃了一点儿面包屑。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>94874</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>100548</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>王后流下了眼泪：“太可怜了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>100548</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>102751</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她看了一眼女儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>102751</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>111590</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>艾伦低着头，她的胸口发出了什么声音。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>111590</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>113813</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>王后的眼睛亮了！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>113813</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>117749</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我的方法有效果了！”她想，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>117749</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>120860</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“公主终于要哭了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>120861</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>131431</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是，艾伦发出的声音不是哭声，而是笑声！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>131431</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>134630</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>过了一会儿，公主再也忍不住了，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>134630</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>138374</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她开始哈哈大笑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>138375</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>144798</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>国王和王后很头疼，让仆人把公主带走了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>144798</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>151366</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们该怎么办？”国王问道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>151366</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156773</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第二天，国王和王后又尝试了其他方法：</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>156773</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>166205</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们上楼来到公主的卧室。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>166205</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>173990</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后他们用最凶的态度、最难听的话骂了公主。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>173990</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>178170</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>公主的嘴唇开始颤抖，然后……</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>178170</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>184657</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她又大笑起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>184657</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>186052</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在这个时候，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>186052</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>190731</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有一位英俊的王子正在为自己寻找妻子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>190731</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>196633</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>王子勇敢善良，有很多女孩儿喜欢他，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>196633</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>203177</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是王子都不喜欢。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>203178</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>208670</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“可能我要去其他王国找找了。”他最后决定，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>208670</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>212851</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“也许我能在那里找到适合我的妻子，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>212851</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>223519</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个能让我开心快乐的妻子。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>223519</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>229702</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一天下午，他骑着马来到一个湖边。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>229702</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>233069</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“多么美丽的湖哇！”王子心想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>233069</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>238094</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊！”有人在尖叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>238094</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>241820</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>王子跳下马，跑到湖边。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>241820</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>246536</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他看到湖中心有一个女孩儿快要淹死了！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>